    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Wheelock Choc. Na.</placeName>
                <date>Feb 3d 1857</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I have made<lb/> arrangements with <persName>A Merwin
                    Esqr.</persName> Agent<lb/> of the Am Board of Com. for Foreign
                    Mysuns<add>?</add> a<lb/> letter for the Occident for the current year<lb/>
                ending in <date>March</date>. At that time you will<lb/> please discontinue sending
                me the work. I<lb/> make this request with <sic>reluctence</sic> as I have<lb/> read
                your publication with interest from its<lb/> commencement but some pecuniary
                pres<lb/>sures seem to render this step necessary. Should<lb/> you continue the work
                &amp; my <sic>circumstences</sic><lb/> be more favorable hereafter I may again<lb/>
                become a subscriber.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I am engaged in translating the Heb<lb/> new scriptures into the
                Choctaw language I<lb/> read the original Hebrew the venerable language<lb/> of your
                forefathers which tends to increase the in<lb/>terest I have <add>?</add> felt in
                the welfare of your<lb/> people. I see from the Occident that you are<lb/> engaged
                in the translation of the Holy Scriptures<lb/> should the work be published, I
                should hope<lb/> if my pecuniary circumstances would admit<lb/> of it to obtain a
                copy.</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Affectionately</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">Alfred Wright</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p><add>?</add> I requested <persName>Mr Merwin</persName> to pay for the<lb/> Occident
                at the office of the Asmonean No <add>?</add><lb/>
                <placeName>Nassau St N York</placeName>.</p>
        </body>
    </text>
